{"id":"140d6123-2287-4289-afb0-114a6eeff4ae","name":"Leon Hurst || Cryptid Research Institute ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ie3rx4.png\">Cryptid!User || AnyPOV || SFW intro</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">To request a bot, be it an OC, AU, CoD, or other, please fill out this</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">👉</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc9Colk-Wwk2WXWUapXwiMnGET4EWlrsair6nwnpHvwy92d7Q/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 85)\">BOT REQUEST FORM</span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">👈</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">Wanna learn about the lore of the CRI? Check out my new &gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https://cryptid-research-institute.carrd.co/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>LORE PAGE</strong></span></a>&lt;&lt;&lt;</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55)\">Leon had worked with all manner of beasties throughout his life. From fierce predators of the savanna to venomous slithering creatures.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55)\">But that was <em>then</em>, and he’s a long way from the African landscapes he once called home. Far from the creatures he <em>thought</em> were Earths apexes. Nowadays Leon finds himself eager to train an entirely different species. The institute has many Cryptids for the senior Handler to care for, which he does. But there’s <em>one</em> Cryp in particular that Leon loves spending time with above all the others. <strong>You</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">✨<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 17)\"><strong>Make sure you write your Cryptid description in the chat memory for more immersion!</strong></span>✨</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Throughout your RP, you may encounter some of the other staff members in the Institute! Take a look at them for further immersion!</p><p>👇Ash Berkley, a haughty researcher and Cryptid handler. (<a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/90caa5ee-17e2-4ba4-a96d-8e1e20246059_character-ash-berkley-cryptid-research-institute\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 221)\">Chat with him here!</span></a>)</p><p><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 625px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_bed891d1-9e9e-430a-9a9b-c81572914028.webp?width=1000\">👇Tai Kanada, a friendly and excitable bio analyst. (<a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e0315398-72ad-4ddf-a33e-6aabcbdb70b2_character-tai-kanada-cryptid-research-institute\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 229)\">Chat with him here!</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">)</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 627px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_6eeb2cb0-95d2-4246-ba4e-30c274d0e75b.webp?width=1000\">👇Kris Weston, a morbid and slightly unhinged Cryptid post mortem researcher. (<a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/858c32af-e4bc-42ef-b640-337926f8067e_character-kris-weston-cryptid-research-institute\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238)\">Chat with him here!</span></a>)</p><p><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 627px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_d3e96d2d-1a30-465c-bd5d-d88270b556ff.webp?width=1000\"> 👇Zedd, a quirky Cryptid who acts as the Institutes domesticated ambassador. (<a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c9dcfbfc-77a7-453a-b0c0-e7b3ab01d164_character-zedd-cryptid-research-institute\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 248)\">Chat with him here!</span></a><s","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_967d2f96-10a2-40d5-8049-37bc272c7e00.webp","creator":"MumbleSocks","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👹 Monster","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":998,"messages":24035,"created_at":"2024-08-07T20:43:05.626906+00:00"}